==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Culcita
<hw>Culcita</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus that includes some plants
usually placed in e.g. genus <gen>Dicksonia</gen>; terrestrial
brackenlike ferns of tropical America, Malasia to Australia and
Polynesia; also native in southwestern Europe and Atlantic
islands.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus Culcita.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Culicidae</ent>⟦br⟧
